@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_uzluoy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((v2 * tmp) / (0.96 - wp.exp(v2 + 0.30)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.abs((v2 + 0.97 * v0 + 0.23)))
    v2 = v2
    tmp = (wp.abs(v2) - 0.37)
    v2 = 0.51
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
